{"tid":831841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日攞部iphone去貼mon貼…","createTime":"2018-09-22T10:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T10:44:56.000Z","uid":46486,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fc56823beb77ffdd5345b4099aef6922aca404c5","tid":831841,"uid":46486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:10:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n啊叔我今日攞住部新買嘅iphone8+去貼mon貼，<br />\n入到去間店到我同個店員講貼mon貼，<br />\n佢講左一大輪野話咩高清、防爆&hellip;<br />\n跟全佢話呢隻好冇？ 我根本唔知佢講邊隻，<br />\n我話冇所謂（心諗mon貼呢啲消耗品，邊隻都冇所謂）<br />\n換完之後佢就同我講左句，乜你唔用機殼架？<br />\n我望一望部太空灰嘅iphone8+,再望一望個店員。<br />\n我講左佢一句，我不嬲都唔用。<br />\n佢呆左，我冇理到佢，攞完部電話頭也不回走出間店到。<br />\n心諗，呢部手機如果加個殼比佢，咁啲電話比人有得選擇唔同嘅顏色咪好多餘？又浪費左設計者嘅心機。<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想問下巴絲們，邊到有平靚正嘅iphone8+嘅殼買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23cdf5065abba4a874d5b480a52a95ab33d9adb9","tid":831841,"uid":163972,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:10:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5a070b1615929c34b5c1994e28122830a4cfa70","tid":831841,"uid":1354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:11:42.000Z","msg":"真係唔好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d5738540f5858356e7eb747d929e5307debc69","tid":831841,"uid":206727,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:12:38.000Z","msg":"越睇越尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49baa6883193e4df3c4835c779e7a0ef90d47b4f","tid":831841,"uid":46486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23cdf5065abba4a874d5b480a52a95ab33d9adb9","tid":831841,"uid":163972,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:10:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" c